# Overall Conclusion

The dashboard indicates that sales performance is influenced by regional differences, customer segments, product categories, discount strategies, shipping efficiency, and return behavior. Leadership should focus on strengthening profitable categories, improving delivery performance, controlling excessive discounting, and addressing high-return areas to support sustainable growth and profitability.
